{"tid":2108799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為發言人對英國政治化決定感到失望及錯誤，將審視在英國的業務。","createTime":"2020-07-14T20:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T01:03:36.000Z","uid":360777,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"af6f8c693ca2da3ec10bb099e2de9546b979d19b","tid":2108799,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T20:28:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537763-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537763-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=1da3f332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537763-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2d819b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537763-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><br />\n英國決定禁止中國電訊設備商華為參與當地5G網絡建設，美國國務卿蓬佩奧在社交網站Twitter貼文稱，英國的決定在5G時代促進跨大西洋的安全，同時保護公民的私隱、國家安全和自由世界價值。<br />\n<br />\n白宮國家安全顧問奧布萊恩表示，英國的行動反映日益增加的共識，即華為和其他不受信任的供應商對國家安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府下令當地電訊公司明年起不可購買華為的5G組件與設備，電訊商要在2027年底之前移除華為的設備。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cfdd15fc9ed7bdcf8293e395e00387550bcd4656","tid":2108799,"uid":360777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T20:29:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>英國傳媒報道，在英國宣布禁用華為數小時前，華為英國董事會主席約翰布朗宣布將於今年9月提前離職。<br />\n<br />\n約翰布朗截至目前在任5年。按照原計劃，他將於明年3月離職。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537758-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537758-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=6eb5de30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537758-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=08f7